        "content": "<p>look at:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Cassidy C, Hébert M, Kelly GM. Reflective subcategories, localizations and factorizationa systems. Journal of the Australian Mathematical Society Series A Pure Mathematics and Statistics. 1985;38(3):287-329. doi:10.1017/S1446788700023624 (available <a href=\"https://www.cambridge.org/core/services/aop-cambridge-core/content/view/0DDCB060FE9EB733D5B2EE94B0DAEF4C/S1446788700023624a.pdf/reflective-subcategories-localizations-and-factorizationa-systems.pdf\">here</a>)</li>\n<li>in particular, the relation between torsion theories and pre-fibrations, explained in Rosicky-Tholen <a href=\"https://www.math.muni.cz/~rosicky/papers/TF2.pdf\">here</a>.</li>\n</ul>",
